{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01BRmD8Ayyz1qyHmPPRAbkNU","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Changelog\n2\t\n3\tAll notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.\n4\t\n5\t## v0.3.3\n6\t- Update dependencies, Go 1.26.5, alpine 3.24\n7\t- Ignore openpgp advisory GO-2026-5932 in govulncheck and trivy (unmaintained by design, no fix)\n8\t\n9\t## v0.3.2\n10\t\n11\t- fix: only append the branch as an image tag when the Config's `spec.image` has no tag\n12\t  already. Previously the resolver always did `image + \":\" + branch`, so a semver-pinned image\n13\t  (`â€¦/agent-claude:v0.1.1`) became an invalid `â€¦:v0.1.1:dev`. Tag detection treats a `:` after\n14\t  the last `/` as an existing tag (registry-port colons excluded; digests preserved). Untagged\n15\t  images (e.g. quant-native `agent-backtest`) still get the branch tag as before. This unblocks\n16\t  semver-pinned agent images rendered by the Helm chart.\n17\t\n18\t## v0.3.1\n19\t\n20\t- refactor: converge build to the `bborbe/kafka-topic-reader` publish-only model â€” `make buca`\n21\t  now builds and pushes `docker.io/bborbe/agent-task-executor:$(VERSION)` (semver from git tag),\n22\t  replacing the private-registry `:$(BRANCH)` flow and the separate `publish` target. Deployment\n23\t  moves to the quant config repo; removed `k8s/*.yaml`, `Makefile.k8s`, `Makefile.env`, and the\n24\t  stage `.env` files (kept `k8s/apis` + `k8s/client` CRD code).\n25\t\n26\t## v0.3.0\n27\t\n28\t- feat: add `make publish` target to build and push a semver-tagged public image to\n29\t  Docker Hub (`docker.io/bborbe/agent-task-executor:<version>`), independent of the\n30\t  private-registry `buca` flow. Pattern mirrors `bborbe/kafka-topic-reader`.\n31\t\n32\t## v0.2.0\n33\t\n34\t- feat: propagate `TOPIC_PREFIX` (from `TopicPrefix` config) to spawned per-task Jobs, alongside the existing\n35\t  `BRANCH` env var, so child agents (agent-claude/code/gemini/pi/sentry-issue-analyzer) can build their Kafka\n36\t  result topics.\n37\t\n38\t## v0.1.0\n39\t\n40\t- feat: add explicit `TopicPrefix` config (`arg:\"topic-prefix\"` / `env:\"TOPIC_PREFIX\"`), replacing the implicit\n41\t  `Branch`-derived Kafka topic prefix. `Branch` (`env:\"BRANCH\"`) is unchanged and keeps its non-topic uses\n42\t  (child-job `BRANCH` env propagation, config image tagging, stage matching). Bumps\n43\t  `github.com/bborbe/agent` to v0.72.0 and `github.com/bborbe/cqrs` to v0.6.0.\n44\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_function_iceqd3zlr1k8_2","session_id":"2797b87b-ab8a-4cea-b290-55a29e5d469e","uuid":"9b90a2ce-28a1-4a55-a077-7f0a9748cc01","timestamp":"2026-07-09T10:42:39.299Z","subagent_type":"dark-factory:prompt-auditor","task_description":"Audit prompt 2 - mount kafka certs"}
